---
title: Bacon, Lemon & Pesto Pasta with Feta & Broccoli
description: The only way to improve the age-old family favourite, pesto pasta, is to add some crispy bacon and creamy feta. With so many textures and well-loved flavours, this dish is sure to please the whole table!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5bd9344630006c784248d212-6e3577ef.jpg
